{"tid":346862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Emilia Wong身邊既人都幾弱智","createTime":"2017-08-04T10:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T05:06:50.000Z","uid":23815,"like":446,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4567e6ed4acb80e26ddaea2db85dce4b863bcea8","tid":346862,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:06:30.000Z","msg":"先唔講你個臭閪又話要女性身體自主<br />\n又話我地香港人物化女性<br />\n跟手轉頭去賣裸照 <br />\n賣唔賣到 ? WFCs <br />\n但你話左比我地聽咩叫面係人地比 架係自己丟<br />\n<br />\n今日見到你個EX 出左篇飛機文幫你護航<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/04/180013_ab7d8808cff5f1fb70803654b88aaf3f.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F04%2F180013_ab7d8808cff5f1fb70803654b88aaf3f.PNG&h=83b038c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當中講到男性可以以體力勞動去賺錢 blah blah blah<br />\n提及到健身教練用滿身肌肉係擺明呃女人錢<br />\n身為一個有牌而且DEGREE讀相關野既健身教練 (非正職) <br />\n望到其實好撚柒鳩嬲 我地考哂ACSM / NASM 既牌先夠膽出黎做<br />\n你老母個傻鳩乜柒都唔識就講到我地一文不值<br />\n我地要幫客人去SET diet + exercise routine <br />\n男女客都有 好多都係男客運動員為左提昇表現先黎搵我地<br />\n<br />\n你就咁一句擺明賺女人錢 ? 姐係我地其實乜都唔識. 操到自己大大隻隻去呃女人錢咋 ? 你知唔知健身教練除左教客好似力威WUCFU去操大隻之外 仲可以教佢地健康減肥 ?<br />\n成個行業係有害群之馬 但你憑有限既認知去肯定哂成個行業 ? <br />\n區議員 ? 仲話想去做立法會 ? 原來係靠無憑無據既證據去夾硬支持自己既道理<br />\n<br />\n你條傻鳩收皮啦 你千奇唔好講你中學同大學讀邊間 <br />\n影撚衰哂果D學校既畢業生呀"},{"pid":"126fdcbb8a0b56fb31aeeae339906d7ced0177a7","tid":346862,"uid":23815,"like":119,"dislike":0,"score":119,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:10:36.000Z","msg":"補多句 <br />\n女人到今時今日唔做得體力勞動既野 咩叫先天性 ? <br />\n咪又係有一大班女人係地盤搵食 你地班女權撚一味就剩係識賴天賴地<br />\n從來無諗過某部份女人係心理上完全覺得呢D唔係自己應該做既工<br />\n所以果部份既女人寧願去做SALES + CS都唔想日曬雨淋 但又要叫辛苦<br />\n又要貪靚但又要叫辛苦 <br />\n不如直接比你地收錢唔洗你地做呀 ? <br />\n根本你班女權撚做既野就係多鳩餘"},{"pid":"02a28b136a6f9824a7bb52828f1517068a31374d","tid":346862,"uid":21423,"like":41,"dislike":211,"score":-170,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:11:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84f82cf7eefe1e1faeb7c22cce5bba64eb7b2c3d","tid":346862,"uid":23815,"like":14,"dislike":201,"score":-187,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:13:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">既<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘅</strong></span><br />\n比<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>畀</strong></span><br />\n野<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘢</strong></span><br />\n地<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>哋</strong></span><br />\n黎<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嚟</strong></span><br />\n左<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>咗</strong></span><br />\n姐係<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>即係</strong></span><br />\n千奇<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>千祈</strong></span><br />\nD<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>啲</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XpxKG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXpxKG.png&h=97dc3c33&s={SIZE}\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n過街老鼠 你返高登玩陣先啦"},{"pid":"a9b399c3597755388732146105cb9372139ae5b8","tid":346862,"uid":122601,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:16:14.000Z","msg":"練大隻人人都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2396438f01856c6214e972aa8317f1cb12d8463","tid":346862,"uid":60148,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:16:14.000Z","msg":"過街老鼠 你返高登玩陣先啦[/quote]<br />\n隻on9真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f9eadaa51ae6d0e3f901715f33a7530521ee8f","tid":346862,"uid":32485,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過街老鼠 你返高登玩陣先啦</blockquote><br />\n咪quote佢啦"},{"pid":"9872f979dae18f03a6e61d115a5c383fda8020fe","tid":346862,"uid":43760,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:17:15.000Z","msg":"你引用件垃圾 好難俾正評你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0090b78de92a0baf12e52ff969d3f643fe6364d0","tid":346862,"uid":55939,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:18:56