14a388ea44819477d54","tid":346862,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>練大隻人人都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n練過未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一日八餐做唔做到？"},{"pid":"8dbeeba85a52806b6c6bc00da460e68216e3f914","tid":346862,"uid":67895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:31:40.000Z","msg":"佢ex一定唔識排版，睇得好撚辛苦<br />\n冇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bf5d6c31af40db1224ec902fa6eb7fbc40f84d","tid":346862,"uid":28031,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"拎健身教練同做雞比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇健身教練公會之類嘅野出嚟屌尻條傻仔"},{"pid":"e5cded91cee452175d985e6774f0554d5a8a0e0d","tid":346862,"uid":743,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295517945c055b170e6a870eebb7be55fffb5d3d","tid":346862,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:44:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎健身教練同做雞比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇健身教練公會之類嘅野出嚟屌尻條傻仔</blockquote><br />\n其實如果佢地將物化呢個term視為中性，就唔止健身教練，係所有工種都會同性工作一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba581bac4202033f535984d3a046fec78be347c","tid":346862,"uid":23815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>練大隻人人都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講既野無錯<br />\n但係我地係教你用最有效同埋最少機會令你受傷既方法<br />\n配合埋飲食係最短時間入面達到你想要既效果 (performance / keep fit / muscular)<br />\n呢個係健身教練既價值所在 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都係算啦 你呢D人講撚完你都係覺得健身教練只係呃錢既人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c4d51772d91bbfd114754c7576d2355ab7bb30","tid":346862,"uid":23815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拎健身教練同做雞比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇健身教練公會之類嘅野出嚟屌尻條傻仔</blockquote><br />\n其實如果佢地將物化呢個term視為中性，就唔止健身教練，係所有工種都會同性工作一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗清楚一樣野<br />\n從來物化緊女性既都係女權人士<br />\n佢地去眨低女性地位從而希望係呢個處於弱勢既位置去搏取人地支持<br />\n呢招手法其實好撚可悲"},{"pid":"ba7b6270462e3459dea8ecad87fc68ea4f13ef64","tid":346862,"uid":15660,"like":11,"dislike":24,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">既<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘅</strong></span><br />\n比<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>畀</strong></span><br />\n野<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘢</strong></span><br />\n地<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>哋</strong></span><br />\n黎<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嚟</strong></span><br />\n左<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>咗</strong></span><br />\n姐係<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>即係</strong></span><br />\n千奇<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>千祈</strong></span><br />\nD<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>啲</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XpxKG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXpxKG.png&h=97dc3c33&s={SIZE}\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n過街老鼠 你返高登玩陣先啦</blockquote><br />\n打錯字仲聲大大 你返高登算喇教練"},{"pid":"1a8e8d7b0642eb0b288f50d9dad4f38a1acbe411","tid":346862,"uid":53687,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拎健身教練同做雞比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇健身教練公會之類嘅野出嚟屌尻條傻仔</blockquote><br />\n其實如果佢地將物化呢個term視為中性，就唔止健身教練，係所有工種都會同性工作一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n身體自主本身係用於防止婦女或兒童被性侵嘅概念，因為受害者無能力去反抗，而施暴者正正係物化咗受害者先唔顧及佢感受。<br />\n某啲女權撚平權平上腦，覺得全世界迫害緊佢，批評下就畀佢話係父權呀、歧視呀，但自知理據薄弱先濫用物化嚟強化自己嘅立論。"},{"pid":"3d88dda1fc5c2ce87d0e3ab206e65fb4b9c27bce","tid":346862,"uid":71502,"like":5,"dislike":16,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">既<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘅</strong></span><br />\n比<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>畀</strong></span><br />\n野<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘢</strong></span><br />\n地<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>哋</strong></span><br />\n黎<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嚟</strong></span><br />\n左<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>咗</strong></span><br />\n姐係<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>即係</strong></span><br />\n千奇<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>千祈</strong></span><br />\nD<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>啲</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XpxKG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXpxKG.png&h=97dc3c33&s={SIZE}\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n過街老鼠 你返高登玩陣先啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2ah4sw91\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2ah4sw91&h=73f853a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e21cae1823f4ea5fc255c9736b1b73cb8300ccd1","tid":346862,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:07:05.000Z","msg":"有得屌你地唔屌！"},{"pid":"aeee6a10fc3b8295274812956c0c150a01aee01a","tid":346862,"uid":3634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T11:09:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>練大隻人人都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講既野無錯<br />\n但係我地係教你用最有效同埋最少機會令你受傷既方法<br />\n配合埋飲食係最短時間入面達到你想要既效果 (performance / keep fit / muscular)<br />\n呢個係健身教練既價值所在 <img src=\